vote.title: Authorize an amendment to an existing lease agreement with Towne Square Market LP to extend the lease agreement for an additional eight years for approximately 8,100 square feet of office and clinic space located at 3302 North Buckner Boulevard, Suites 124 and 130, to be used as a Women, Infants and Children Clinic for the period June 1, 2022 through May 31, 2030 - Not to exceed $1,173,892.80 - Financing: Health and Human Services Commission Grant Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
